  .hero__body
    .hero__body__inner
      .hero__heading
        img.space--bottom-5.wow.bounceIn src="/images/read.png" alt="Read content"
        h2
          | Read!
      .hero__text
        p
          | Connected services interact with the Reader via API calls that provide a view. Users can access their rendered ebooks through that view, via desktop or mobile browser.
        p
          | The Reader makes a view based on custom settings (i.e. a 10% preview or the whole content for just one month etc.)
